3100, "(fr)You allowed a significant part of the Shivan force to escape.  Although we were successful in neutralizing most of the Shivan supply line, the surviving ships will undoubtedly cause trouble for our forces later on.  Your failure will cost us lives and ships we should not have to lose."

3101, "(fr)Disabling the freighters will prevent them from escaping.  Alternatively, use Disruptor Missiles to temporarily knock out their systems."

3102, "(fr)Excellent work, pilot.  Your performance in this mission was outstanding.  Shivan supply lines to Ikeya have been cut off and we now have full control over this subspace node."

3103, "(fr)Good work, pilot.  Our containment operation was effective in neutralizing most of the Shivan supply line.  The few surviving ships are unlikely to provide significant reinforcement to the Shivan position in Ikeya.  Still, GTI prides itself on going above and beyond the call of duty, and our failure to destroy every ship mars our record somewhat."

3104, "(fr)You also destroyed all hostile targets, including several fighter wings and the Cain cruiser Maus.  You and your wingmen are to be commended for this accomplishment."

3105, "(fr)Unfortunately, not all the cargo was recovered.  Some of our recovery craft were destroyed by the Shivan cruisers.  With the Shivans being destroyed or disappearing all over Terran-Vasudan space, we must gather all the data about them we can while we still have the opportunity."

