3735, "(fr)This is Admiral Amentep of the PVD Guardian.  Allied Terran vessels, please respond."

3736, "(fr)This is Admiral Tess of the GTD Soyakaze.  Greetings, Admiral.  I was not aware that the Guardian had been repaired yet."

3737, "(fr)Regrettably, it has not.  We are still in orbit around Cygnus Prime.  But let us dispense with protocol, for the time is short.  Am I correct in assuming that you have engaged the GTI destroyer Hades?"

3738, "(fr)Affirmative, Admiral.  Our bombers are attacking the Hades near Deneb III."

3739, "(fr)And so the circle completes itself.  Remarkable.  I wish to inform you, Admiral, that one of our fighter squadrons just repelled a Hammer of Light ambush against the GTC Orff and two bomber wings."

3740, "(fr)These craft had entered the Deneb system in an attempt to engage the Hades, but were apparently provided incorrect information by a traitor sympathetic to the GTI.  If you will transmit your coordinates, I will redeploy the Orff and its wings to your location."

3741, "(fr)Transmitting now.  Admiral Amentep, you have our sincerest gratitude."

3742, "(fr)The gratitude is ours, but you may repay us by recounting the story of your victory over the GTI.  Sa Terra, vessels of the GTA.  Admiral Amentep out."

